name: FizzBuzz
description: Print numbers from 1 to N. For multiples of 3 print Fizz, for multiples of 5 print Buzz, for multiples of both print FizzBuzz, otherwise print the number.

io_format.output: N lines, each line contains Fizz, Buzz, FizzBuzz, or the number.

tests.output:
1
2
Fizz
4
Buzz
Fizz
7
8
Fizz
Buzz
11
Fizz
13
14
FizzBuzz
